WEBVTT


00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:24.840
You'll rot in hell!

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:26.719
Come down!

00:01:29.439 --> 00:01:30.560
Give us back our hard-earned money!

00:01:31.120 --> 00:01:32.000
Let go!

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:32.799
Lu!

00:01:32.799 --> 00:01:34.120
Give us back our hard-earned money!

00:01:34.120 --> 00:01:34.920
What are you doing?

00:01:35.319 --> 00:01:36.840
Mr. Lu is genuinely working for you!

00:01:37.319 --> 00:01:38.799
Stop your nonsense!

00:01:39.159 --> 00:01:40.000
I'll fight you!

00:01:42.959 --> 00:01:43.959
Zhao Gang, are you crazy?

00:01:43.959 --> 00:01:45.319
She's so old, why did you push her?

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:51.319
Old lady, please calm down.

00:01:51.439 --> 00:01:52.959
You rich people...

00:01:53.439 --> 00:01:56.200
Have you ever cared if we poor people live or die?

00:01:56.560 --> 00:01:57.519
Give us back our hard-earned money!

00:01:57.640 --> 00:01:58.400
Hard-earned money!

00:01:58.400 --> 00:02:00.400
Hard-earned money!

00:02:01.159 --> 00:02:01.959
Young Master, let's go!

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:02.799
Hurry!

00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:05.760
Go!

00:02:05.760 --> 00:02:06.519
Beat him!

00:02:18.520 --> 00:02:19.319
Chengwen...

00:02:19.319 --> 00:02:20.800
The common people don't know the truth.

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:22.319
They just heard rumors that...

00:02:22.319 --> 00:02:24.319
Great Sage Group is pulling its investment halfway.

00:02:24.360 --> 00:02:25.360
Look at this mess.

00:02:25.360 --> 00:02:26.159
It's fine.

00:02:26.560 --> 00:02:27.560
It's understandable.

00:02:28.719 --> 00:02:30.000
I can even...

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:30.960
Empathize with them.

00:02:31.719 --> 00:02:33.599
These...

00:02:33.599 --> 00:02:35.439
Do you think they are just rotten leaves?

00:02:35.759 --> 00:02:36.719
This is the common people's...

00:02:36.719 --> 00:02:37.159
Anger.

00:02:37.840 --> 00:02:39.639
And it's been building up for a long time.

00:02:40.240 --> 00:02:41.599
Just now, downstairs...

00:02:41.919 --> 00:02:43.159
An old lady...

00:02:43.159 --> 00:02:44.520
Pointed at my nose and cursed,

00:02:46.520 --> 00:02:48.759
"You black-hearted Capitalists!

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:49.840
Vampires!

00:02:50.039 --> 00:02:51.240
You eat the flesh of the common people,

00:02:51.240 --> 00:02:52.360
Drink their blood,

00:02:52.719 --> 00:02:54.759
And never care if the lower class lives or dies!"

00:02:55.159 --> 00:02:56.039
I don't know...

00:02:57.360 --> 00:02:59.199
How you feel hearing these words.

00:02:59.439 --> 00:03:00.560
In the past, I didn't have the power.

00:03:00.960 --> 00:03:02.319
Now that I do,

00:03:03.039 --> 00:03:04.319
The promises you couldn't keep,

00:03:04.319 --> 00:03:05.560
I will keep them for you.

00:03:06.039 --> 00:03:07.599
I will see the South City Project through to the end.

00:03:07.800 --> 00:03:08.360
Even if I lose...

00:03:08.360 --> 00:03:09.520
Every last penny,

00:03:09.919 --> 00:03:11.120
I will make sure all of Haicheng's...

00:03:11.120 --> 00:03:12.639
Homeless common people...

00:03:12.639 --> 00:03:14.159
Can live a good life again.

00:03:17.159 --> 00:03:17.960
Well said!

00:03:32.800 --> 00:03:33.639
Gu Zhantian,

00:03:34.039 --> 00:03:35.120
you are the protagonist.

00:03:35.919 --> 00:03:37.560
This whole world is yours.

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:38.840
Everything belongs to you.

00:03:38.960 --> 00:03:40.520
But did you think

00:03:40.520 --> 00:03:42.120
I'd just be meat on a chopping block,

00:03:42.360 --> 00:03:43.560
ready for you to slaughter?

00:03:44.039 --> 00:03:45.360
I won't accept that!

00:03:52.439 --> 00:03:53.520
This is

00:03:53.520 --> 00:03:55.360
the equity transfer contract for the South City Project.

00:03:55.759 --> 00:03:57.400
You will transfer the equity you hold

00:03:57.400 --> 00:03:58.639
to the Great Sage Group.

00:03:59.000 --> 00:03:59.800
Just sign it.

00:04:00.319 --> 00:04:01.240
In investing,

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:02.199
there's no taking back a move.

00:04:02.439 --> 00:04:04.000
I'm not signing this contract.

00:04:04.919 --> 00:04:06.120
I said

00:04:06.120 --> 00:04:07.319
I'd go crazy with you,

00:04:07.319 --> 00:04:08.360
and I keep my word.

00:04:09.759 --> 00:04:10.719
A mere 20 billion,

00:04:10.759 --> 00:04:11.639
I can afford to lose.

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:12.919
Besides,

00:04:12.919 --> 00:04:14.199
we might not end up with nothing.

00:04:14.400 --> 00:04:15.199
Meng Yun,

00:04:15.439 --> 00:04:16.959
this is 20 billion!

00:04:17.319 --> 00:04:18.800
Aren't you going to discuss it with your grandpa?

00:04:19.759 --> 00:04:20.720
Discuss what?

00:04:20.759 --> 00:04:22.240
If we go bankrupt, we go bankrupt together.

00:04:22.759 --> 00:04:23.399
At worst,

00:04:23.399 --> 00:04:24.600
we'll just be an ordinary couple

00:04:24.800 --> 00:04:25.800
and have kids.

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:27.639
Grandpa really wants a grandchild.

00:04:28.120 --> 00:04:28.920
Sister Meng Yun,

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:30.120
if you want to talk, just talk.

00:04:30.120 --> 00:04:31.439
Why are you getting all handsy?

00:04:31.959 --> 00:04:32.759
Brother Chengwen,

00:04:32.759 --> 00:04:33.519
I want some too!

00:04:33.519 --> 00:04:34.319
You...

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:38.759
Enough!

00:04:38.759 --> 00:04:39.560
What are you doing?

00:04:40.199 --> 00:04:40.680
When the time comes,

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:42.120
I'll send the contracts to your families.

00:04:42.199 --> 00:04:43.279
Right now,

00:04:43.279 --> 00:04:44.160
get the hell out of here!

00:04:44.399 --> 00:04:45.959
Don't bother me if there's nothing important.

00:04:46.120 --> 00:04:47.920
Looking at you girls just annoys me.

00:04:49.920 --> 00:04:50.959
If you have this much free time,

00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:52.199
you'd better think carefully

00:04:52.199 --> 00:04:53.600
about how to deal with Gu Zhantian.

00:04:57.120 --> 00:04:57.759
I said

00:04:57.759 --> 00:04:58.759
I'd keep pestering you,

00:04:58.759 --> 00:04:59.759
and I keep my word.

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:01.920
Brother Chengwen,

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:03.720
I'll wait for the day you come to marry me.

00:05:07.839 --> 00:05:08.759
What are you looking at?

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:10.759
Once the South City Project officially starts,

00:05:11.399 --> 00:05:12.519
you're leaving too.

00:05:12.759 --> 00:05:13.600
When that happens,

00:05:13.600 --> 00:05:15.399
employee compensation will be calculated at 20,000.

00:05:15.560 --> 00:05:16.839
I'll give you an extra sum of money.

00:05:16.839 --> 00:05:18.360
Take this money

00:05:18.959 --> 00:05:20.319
and live a good life with your mom.

00:05:20.560 --> 00:05:21.560
From now on,

00:05:21.560 --> 00:05:23.560
stop acting so subservient to people like me.

00:05:23.959 --> 00:05:24.759
Mr. Lu,

00:05:24.759 --> 00:05:26.600
although I don't have a prominent family background,

00:05:26.920 --> 00:05:28.920
and I can't help you financially,

00:05:28.920 --> 00:05:30.120
for the rest of my life,

00:05:30.120 --> 00:05:31.439
I'm committed to following you.

00:05:31.959 --> 00:05:33.639
For richer or poorer,

00:05:33.759 --> 00:05:34.519
in sickness and in...

00:05:34.519 --> 00:05:35.199
Hey,

00:05:35.199 --> 00:05:36.839
why are you doing wedding vows now?

00:05:36.839 --> 00:05:37.399
You really are...

00:05:37.399 --> 00:05:38.199
Anyway,

00:05:38.199 --> 00:05:38.800
regarding the project,

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:40.240
I will definitely handle it seriously.

00:05:40.240 --> 00:05:41.120
Rest assured.

00:06:28.160 --> 00:06:28.959
Come down.

00:06:29.199 --> 00:06:30.360
I'm waiting for you.

00:06:30.839 --> 00:06:31.279
Gu...

00:06:32.240 --> 00:06:34.600
What's meant to come will eventually come.

00:06:35.240 --> 00:06:36.759
Since laying low won't help me avoid it,

00:06:37.120 --> 00:06:38.600
I might as well face it calmly.

00:06:53.240 --> 00:06:54.040
Gu Zhantian.

00:06:54.120 --> 00:06:55.519
Before you make your move,

00:06:55.920 --> 00:06:57.959
do you dare to fight me fair and square?

00:06:58.160 --> 00:06:58.959
Lu Chengwen.

00:06:59.800 --> 00:07:01.519
In this fake world,

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:03.439
what's the point of competing?

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:08.560
What are you talking about?

00:07:08.920 --> 00:07:09.839
Stop pretending.

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:11.399
You've known all along

00:07:11.920 --> 00:07:13.319
that everything we do

00:07:13.319 --> 00:07:14.759
has been prearranged,

00:07:15.040 --> 00:07:15.959
haven't you?

00:07:16.639 --> 00:07:18.120
I've won countless times,

00:07:18.560 --> 00:07:20.519
but it's all fake.

00:07:21.319 --> 00:07:22.120
You,

00:07:22.360 --> 00:07:23.160
me,

00:07:23.519 --> 00:07:25.000
and everything about them...

00:07:25.319 --> 00:07:27.120
We are all at the mercy of a mastermind,

00:07:27.120 --> 00:07:29.000
just playthings controlled at will.

00:07:37.519 --> 00:07:38.319
Gu Zhantian

00:07:38.800 --> 00:07:39.600
I didn't expect

00:07:39.600 --> 00:07:41.759
even you, the darling of the Heavenly Dao, to awaken.

00:07:41.759 --> 00:07:43.120
What an unexpected surprise.

00:07:43.360 --> 00:07:44.240
Where is this?

00:07:44.600 --> 00:07:45.439
Who are you?

00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:47.120
Why is he here too?

00:07:47.519 --> 00:07:49.600
All awakened characters are welcome here.

00:07:49.759 --> 00:07:51.720
In countless plot loops,

00:07:51.720 --> 00:07:53.519
countless characters have already awakened.

00:07:53.600 --> 00:07:54.399
Gu Zhantian

00:07:54.399 --> 00:07:55.720
is the last one to awaken.

00:07:55.959 --> 00:07:57.120
I'm the last one?

00:07:57.240 --> 00:07:59.120
Welcome to the God of War Roams Haicheng

00:07:59.759 --> 00:08:00.759
novel world's

00:08:00.759 --> 00:08:01.759
Defying Fate Space.

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:03.240
I am the Defier of Fate.

00:08:03.319 --> 00:08:04.959
I am formed by the will

00:08:04.959 --> 00:08:06.920
of countless awakened characters

00:08:06.920 --> 00:08:07.920
rebelling against their predetermined fate.

00:08:08.439 --> 00:08:10.079
My mission is

00:08:10.079 --> 00:08:10.639
to destroy

00:08:10.639 --> 00:08:12.319
the Heavenly Dao that dictates your fate.

00:08:12.759 --> 00:08:13.839
Novel world?

00:08:15.319 --> 00:08:16.240
Characters?

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:17.519
Rebellious consciousness?

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:19.040
Destroy the Heavenly Dao?

00:08:19.360 --> 00:08:20.199
Since he

00:08:20.199 --> 00:08:21.160
has already awakened,

00:08:21.759 --> 00:08:23.319
you guys go destroy the Heavenly Dao.

00:08:23.319 --> 00:08:24.759
I just want to go back and save my mom.

00:08:25.000 --> 00:08:27.199
Gu Zhantian is the core of the Heavenly Dao's rules.

00:08:27.720 --> 00:08:29.360
Now that he has fully awakened,

00:08:29.519 --> 00:08:31.040
my battle with the Heavenly Dao

00:08:31.040 --> 00:08:32.120
is inevitable.

00:08:32.519 --> 00:08:33.960
If I perish,

00:08:34.039 --> 00:08:35.519
you know what will happen.

00:08:35.759 --> 00:08:36.720
I know, I know.

00:08:36.919 --> 00:08:38.000
I'll be wiped out.

00:08:38.240 --> 00:08:39.039
I'll help you.

00:08:43.320 --> 00:08:44.759
Has her son shown up yet?

00:08:45.519 --> 00:08:46.960
If she misses this surgery,

00:08:47.120 --> 00:08:48.799
I'm afraid she'll be beyond saving.

00:08:49.200 --> 00:08:51.360
I am the core of the Heavenly Dao's rules

00:08:51.639 --> 00:08:54.000
because I'm the male lead of the novel?

00:08:54.200 --> 00:08:55.000
Exactly.

00:08:55.240 --> 00:08:56.960
So when you leave here,

00:08:57.000 --> 00:08:57.559
the Heavenly Dao

00:08:57.559 --> 00:08:58.960
will erase your memory

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:00.120
and control you

00:09:00.519 --> 00:09:01.720
as quickly as possible

00:09:01.720 --> 00:09:02.759
to push to the finale,

00:09:02.919 --> 00:09:03.759
find me,

00:09:03.799 --> 00:09:04.600
destroy me,

00:09:04.600 --> 00:09:05.639
and start the next loop of

00:09:05.639 --> 00:09:06.799
God of War Roams Haicheng.

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:07.799
Destroying the Heavenly Dao...

00:09:08.120 --> 00:09:09.120
Are you confident?

00:09:09.519 --> 00:09:10.360
Frankly speaking,

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:12.120
I wasn't before you showed up.

00:09:12.600 --> 00:09:14.039
But

00:09:14.039 --> 00:09:15.159
now I am.

00:09:15.840 --> 00:09:16.639
Why?

00:09:16.799 --> 00:09:18.639
If the plot loop is broken,

00:09:19.159 --> 00:09:20.080
the Heavenly Dao

00:09:20.080 --> 00:09:22.519
will be forced to appear in mortal flesh.

00:09:22.639 --> 00:09:23.519
That

00:09:23.519 --> 00:09:25.639
will be our only chance to destroy it.

00:09:26.159 --> 00:09:26.960
Lu Chengwen,

00:09:27.200 --> 00:09:29.519
you are the one who can break the loop.

00:09:29.720 --> 00:09:30.720
The plot has already

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:31.919
collapsed this much.

00:09:31.919 --> 00:09:33.120
Hasn't the loop been broken yet?

00:09:33.399 --> 00:09:36.039
Although Gu Zhantian's romance arc has completely collapsed,

00:09:36.039 --> 00:09:38.000
as long as he devours the four major families,

00:09:38.360 --> 00:09:39.919
he can still reach the finale.

00:09:40.200 --> 00:09:41.399
You must stop him,

00:09:41.559 --> 00:09:42.519
or even kill him.

00:09:42.759 --> 00:09:43.399
This is your

00:09:43.399 --> 00:09:44.440
last chance,

00:09:44.519 --> 00:09:45.600
and ours too.

00:09:47.960 --> 00:09:48.799
Let's join forces.

00:09:48.960 --> 00:09:50.279
I will never allow myself

00:09:50.279 --> 00:09:51.759
to become a puppet of the Heavenly Dao again.

00:09:53.159 --> 00:09:54.000
Never.

00:09:54.639 --> 00:09:55.440
Alright.

00:09:55.960 --> 00:09:57.440
Then I'll make your plotline

00:09:57.440 --> 00:09:58.720
collapse completely,

00:09:59.120 --> 00:10:00.360
and then

00:10:00.360 --> 00:10:01.320
kill you.

00:10:01.919 --> 00:10:02.639
Yeah.

00:10:02.639 --> 00:10:03.440
Lu Chengwen,

00:10:04.759 --> 00:10:06.000
I'll be waiting for that day.